&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;Normal (Web)&quot;&gt;As a (Senior) Talent Acquisition Specialist, you will be working on a range of requisition, from entry-level to senior, technical and&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;Normal (Web)&quot;&gt;scientific roles within our R&amp;amp;D teams across the US and UK. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;Normal (Web)&quot;&gt;You’ll&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;Normal (Web)&quot;&gt; support hiring managers throughout the recruitment process, from job scoping and sourcing to &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;Normal (Web)&quot;&gt;selection&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;Normal (Web)&quot;&gt;, ensuring a seamless experience for candidates and &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;Normal (Web)&quot;&gt;accurate&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;Normal (Web)&quot;&gt; data in our ATS. Success in this role requires a strong understanding of Compass’s mission and research focus, enabling you to attract and engage top-tier talent who align with our purpose and values.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&g
